Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 05 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Cartilage lesion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Traumatic' radio button is enabled
And 'Degenerative' radio button is enabled

When I click on the localizer
And I select all 6 zones on the localizer
Then all 6 zones are selected and turn red

When I select 'Traumatic' radio button
Then 'Contusion' radio button is enabled
And 'Delamination' radio button is enabled
And 'Cartilage flap' radio button is enabled
And 'Cartilage flake' radio button is enabled
And 'Fissure' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Degenerative' radio button
Then 'Grade I' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade II' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade III' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade IV' radio button is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled

And 'Subchondral cysts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Intra-articular loose body' checkbox is enabled
And 'Chondrocalcinosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Acetabulum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Femur' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Intra-articular loose body' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled







And 'Tear' checkbox is enabled
And 'Degeneration' checkbox is enabled
And 'Paralabral cyst' checkbox is enabled

And 'Labral plica' radio button is enabled
And 'Femoral neck plica' radio button is enabled
And 'Ligamental plica' radio button is enabled

And 'Inclination' input field is enabled
And 'Dysplasia' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Tear' checkbox
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Partial' radio button is enabled
And 'Complete' radio button is enabled
And 'Delamination' radio button is enabled
And 'Associated cartilage lesion' checkbox is enabled

When I click on the localizer
And I select all 6 zones on the localizer
Then all 6 zones are selected and turn red

When I select 'Degeneration' checkbox
Then 'Mucoid' radio button is enabled
And 'Ossified' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Paralabral cyst' checkbox
Then 'Max. size' input field is enabled

When I select 'Tear' checkbox
Then 'Femoral head' checkbox is enabled
And 'Acetabulum' checkbox is enabled
